  description="김민찬 FE Developer 연락처 — 이메일, GitHub, Velog"
>
  <section class="space-y-4">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">Contact</h1>
    <p class="max-w-3xl text-slate-300">
      이직·협업·프로젝트 관련 문의는 아래 채널로 연락 주세요. Case Study를 먼저 보시고 궁금한 점이 있으면
      편하게 메일 주셔도 됩니다.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-10 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
    <a href="mailto:ydjm1994@gmail.com" class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-5">
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Email</p>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm font-semibold">ydjm1994@gmail.com</p>
    </a>
    <a href="tel:01099573068" class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-5">
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Phone</p>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm font-semibold">010-9957-3068</p>
    </a>
    <a href="https://github.com/mucho7" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-5">
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">GitHub</p>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm font-semibold">github.com/mucho7</p>
    </a>
    <a href="https://velog.io/@kimjih94/posts" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900 p-5">
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-400">Blog</p>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm font-semibold">velog.io/@kimjih94/posts</p>
    </a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
